## 一、授权分级（核心条款） / Article 1 — Tiered Authorization (Core Terms)

在遵守本协议全部限制的前提下，本作品按使用主体与用途授予以下两类权限：
Subject to all restrictions herein, the Work is granted under two tiers based on the user and purpose:

### 1.1 个人研究免费许可 / Free Individual Research License
任何自然人（个人）可免费将本作品用于非商业的学术研究、学习或个人实验。
Any natural person (individual) may use the Work free of charge for non-commercial academic research, study, or personal experimentation.

允许 / Permitted:
- 为上述研究、学习目的，下载、复制、编译、运行、修改本作品；
  Download, copy, compile, run, and modify the Work for the above research or study purposes;
- 在学术成果（论文、报告）中引用本作品并注明出处。
  Cite the Work in academic outputs (papers, reports) with proper attribution.

禁止（违反即视为超出本许可范围） / Prohibited (breach constitutes exceeding this license):
- 用于任何商业目的（包括但不限于产品销售、服务提供、盈利性咨询）；
  Any commercial purpose (including but not limited to product sales, service provision, or profitable consulting);
- 为任何企业、政府机构或事业单位提供基于本作品的服务、交付物或内部能力；
  Providing services, deliverables, or internal capability based on the Work to any enterprise, government agency, or public institution;
- 将修改后的版本用于上述禁止用途，或再行分发以消除本声明；
  Using modified versions for the prohibited purposes above, or redistributing to remove this notice;
- 移除或篡改本作品中的任何版权、商标或许可声明。
  Removing or altering any copyright, trademark, or license notice in the Work.

### 1.2 政府 / 企业商业授权 / Government / Enterprise Commercial License
任何政府机构、事业单位、企业或商业组织（统称"商业使用者"）拟将本作品用于任何目的（包括但不限于内部部署、产品研发、服务提供、商业研究、教学培训），必须事先取得权利人的书面付费授权。
Any government agency, public institution, enterprise, or commercial organization (collectively, the "Commercial User") intending to use the Work for any purpose (including but not limited to internal deployment, product development, service provision, commercial research, or training) must obtain prior written paid authorization from the Rights Holder.

- 在签署《商业授权协议》并支付约定费用之前，商业使用者不得复制、部署、运行、集成、修改或分发本作品，亦不得使其员工或关联方代为实施上述行为。
  Before signing a Commercial Authorization Agreement and paying the agreed fee, the Commercial User shall not copy, deploy, run, integrate, modify, or distribute the Work, nor cause its employees or affiliates to do so.
- 授权范围、地域、期限、费用、技术支持与限制，以双方另行签署的书面协议为准。
  Scope, territory, term, fees, technical support, and restrictions are governed by a separate written agreement between the parties.
- 未经授权的商业使用构成侵权，权利人保留追究法律责任及索赔的权利。
  Unauthorized commercial use constitutes infringement; the Rights Holder reserves the right to pursue legal liability and claims.

