## 四、通用条款 / Article 4 — General Terms

**4.1 无其他授权 / No Other Rights.** 除本协议明示授予者外，不授予任何明示或默示的权利（包括专利权、商标权的任何许可）。 No rights are granted other than those expressly stated herein (including any license of patent or trademark rights).

**4.2 无担保 / No Warranty.** 本作品按"现状"提供，不作任何明示或默示担保，包括但不限于对适销性、特定用途适用性及不侵权的担保。 The Work is provided "as is" without any express or implied warranty, including any warranty of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement.

**4.3 责任限制 / Limitation of Liability.** 无论何种情形，权利人对因使用或不能使用本作品所致的任何间接、特殊、附带或后果性损害不承担责任。 In no event shall the Rights Holder be liable for any indirect, special, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use or inability to use the Work.

**4.4 终止 / Termination.** 任何主体若违反本协议，其获得的所有许可自违反之日起自动终止；终止后须立即停止使用并销毁所有副本。 Any breach automatically terminates all licenses granted; upon termination, use must cease and all copies destroyed.

**4.5 商标 / Trademarks.** 本协议不授予任何商标使用权。"Nohn""第二视角"等标识的 ™/® 权利均归相关权利人所有。 No trademark rights are granted; the ™/® marks such as "Nohn" and "Second Perspective" belong to their respective owners.

**4.6 适用法律与管辖 / Governing Law and Jurisdiction.** 依第二条（许可人确定与适用法律）之约定确定。 As determined by Article 2.

**4.7 可分割性 / Severability.** 任一条款被认定无效，不影响其余条款效力。 If any provision is held invalid, the remainder of this Agreement remains effective.

**4.8 完整协议 / Entire Agreement.** 本协议构成双方就本作品授权的完整约定，取代此前所有口头或书面沟通。 This Agreement is the entire understanding between the parties regarding the authorization of the Work and supersedes all prior oral or written communications.

